    <!-- INTRO: SWEDISH CANDY CULTURE -->

    <p>Swedish gummies are no longer a niche import — they are one of the fastest-growing candy categories in the United States. Driven by viral TikTok unboxings, the clean-ingredient movement, and a genuine fascination with Scandinavian food culture, American consumers are discovering what Swedes have known for decades: their candy is simply better. No high-fructose corn syrup. No synthetic dyes. Unique shapes like skulls, fish, and Viking helmets. And a texture — firm, chewy, satisfying — that most American gummies cannot replicate. This guide ranks the 10 best Swedish gummies available in the US in 2026, from iconic classics to premium imports.</p>

