    <p>Candy People is one of the premier Swedish candy brands that has made serious inroads into the American market — and their Gummy Skulls are the best introduction to authentic Scandinavian sour candy. Made in Sweden using potato starch instead of gelatin, these skull-shaped gummies deliver a firm, satisfying chew with a sour coating that hits immediately but mellows into fruity sweetness. The ingredient list is remarkably clean: no artificial colors, no gelatin, no high-fructose corn syrup. This is exactly what sets Swedish gummies apart from American sour candy brands. If you enjoy <a href="/candy/best-sour-gummies/">sour gummies</a>, these offer a completely different flavor experience than domestic options — less aggressive acidity, more nuanced fruit flavor underneath.</p>

